VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'simple. Then, on your dashboard, you can start up a new app with a blank canvas. Now, since this isn\'t a full-blown tutorial, I will just choose the preset Postgres database, but you can see here all the options we really have that we'

[01:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'can build into this, which is really nice. Once I have a database and my case Postgres is linked, we\'re done. In the database, there are a bunch of tables you can play with, but I\'m going to choose the employees table, as this'

